ZH: 我只吃了半个苹果。
EN: I only ate half an apple.

ZH: 他们只来了半个小时。
EN: They only stayed for half an hour.

ZH: 这个杯子只装了半杯水。
EN: This cup only contains half a cup of water.

ZH: 我工作了半天。
EN: I worked for half a day.

ZH: 明天我只有半天的时间。
EN: I only have half a day tomorrow.

ZH: 我的房租只需要半个月。
EN: My rent only requires half a month.

ZH: 她只写了半页作业。
EN: She only wrote half a page of homework.

ZH: 我们还有半年的时间准备。
EN: We have half a year to prepare.

ZH: 我们这里有半天的时间。
EN: We have half a day here.

ZH: 你只有半个小时完成这个任务。
EN: You have only half an hour to complete this task.

ZH: 半数学期已经过去了。
EN: Half the semester has already passed.

ZH: 我只有半张车票。
EN: I have only half a train ticket.

ZH: 半年级的学生还太小。
EN: Students in the first grade are still too young.

ZH: 我的新手机只有半年保修期。
EN: My new phone only has a six-month warranty.

ZH: 半数人认为这是个好主意。
EN: Half of the people think it's a good idea.

ZH: 我只写了半句话。
EN: I only wrote half a sentence.

ZH: 老师只看了半个答案。
EN: The teacher only looked at half the answer.

ZH: 半程马拉松是21.1公里。
EN: A half marathon is 21.1 kilometers.

ZH: 我只收到半个工资。
EN: I only received half the salary.

ZH: 还剩下半页纸。
EN: There's still half a page of paper left.
